.com/4-reasons-to-visit-the-english-riviera/\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"179\" src=\"/images/posts/buckfast-butterflies-english-riviera-300x179.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium wp-image-3529\" alt=\"Buckfast Butterflies English Riviera\" srcset=\"/images/posts/buckfast-butterflies-english-riviera-300x179.jpg 300w, /images/posts/buckfast-butterflies-english-riviera-1024x610.jpg 1024w, /images/posts/buckfast-butterflies-english-riviera-768x457.jpg 768w, /images/posts/buckfast-butterflies-english-riviera-320x191.jpg 320w, /images/posts/buckfast-butterflies-english-riviera-640x381.jpg 640w, /images/posts/buckfast-butterflies-english-riviera-360x214.jpg 360w, /images/posts/buckfast-butterflies-english-riviera-720x429.jpg 720w, /images/posts/buckfast-butterflies-english-riviera-1080x643.jpg 1080w, /images/posts/buckfast-butterflies-english-riviera-800x476.jpg 800w, /images/posts/buckfast-butterflies-english-riviera.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\">\n\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<h3>\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://travelplaninfo.com/4-reasons-to-visit-the-english-riviera/\">\n\t\t\t\t4 Reasons To Visit The English Riviera\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<p>The English Riviera is a perfect place to take a break from the hustle and bustle of every day life.  Not only do you benefit from the beauty of South Devon, but there are also a wide variety of places to visit and things to do.</p>\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t<a href=\"https://travelplaninfo.com/4-reasons-to-visit-the-english-riviera/\" aria-label=\"Read more about 4 Reasons To Visit The English Riviera\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n\t\t\tRead More »\t\t</a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-load-more-anchor\" data-page=\"1\" data-max-page=\"4\" data-next-page=\"https://travelplaninfo.com/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/page/2/?per_page=100&amp;_fields=id%2Cslug%2Ctitle%2Cexcerpt%2Ccontent%2Cdate%2Cmodified%2Ccategories%2Ctags%2Cfeat